00:01:25.335 --> 00:01:28.004 position:50% align:center
[DUKE] "I'm sorry to report
that this wretched curse,

00:01:28.088 --> 00:01:30.423 position:50% align:center
which takes the life's breath
of any unfortunate thing

00:01:30.507 --> 00:01:34.260 position:50% align:center
