shows no sign of breaking."

00:01:34.344 --> 00:01:37.681 position:50% align:center
[MAID] My Lady, another
animal touched the boy and...

00:01:37.764 --> 00:01:39.432 position:50% align:center
[MOM] Living under
the same roof with him

00:01:39.516 --> 00:01:41.393 position:50% align:center
