00:01:41.476 --> 00:01:43.019 position:50% align:center
Send him to our villa.

00:01:43.103 --> 00:01:45.980 position:50% align:center
That child is like
Death incarnate.

00:01:47.148 --> 00:01:48.817 position:50% align:center
[DUKE]
"I don't understand.

00:01:48.900 --> 00:01:51.695 position:50% align:center
Why did the witch
put this curse on me?"

00:02:07.127 --> 00:02:09.295 position:50% align:center
[DUKE] "There is something
else that troubles me.

00:02:09.379 --> 00:02:11.756 position:50% align:center
A lot. And that's..."

00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:12.632 position:50% align:center
